README for xfce 4.6.x

REQUIREMENTS

PRE-INSTALL

  Be sure that you don't have xfce 4.4.x installed, or remove it.

POST-INSTALL

PRECAUTION

  Update/install ports in the following order:
   
    - libxfce4util
    - libxfcegui4
    - libxfce4menu
    - xfconf
    - all the rest ...
    
  or use prt-get:

    prt-get update `prt-get quickdep xfce4`
